                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm" data-i18n="featureDetailDesc2">Download videos in their original quality including 4K, 1440p, 1080p HD, or extract audio in MP3 format up to 320kbps.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-800/30 rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-700/50">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-3">
                            <div class="bg-green-600/20 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-shield text-green-400"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white" data-i18n="featureDetail3">100% Private</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm" data-i18n="featureDetailDesc3">We don't store your downloads or track your activity. Your privacy is our top priority with no logs kept.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-800/30 rounded-xl p-5 border border-slate-700/50">
                        <div class="flex items-start mb-3">
                            <div class="bg-blue-600/20 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3">
                                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-blue-400"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white" data-i18n="featureDetail4">Works On All Devices</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm" data-i18n="featureDetailDesc4">Download directly to your phone, tablet or computer. Our service works perfectly on iOS, Android, Windows and Mac.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

